    ],
    "http://ogp.me/ns#title": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "Montreal Guitar Trio | Christmas Around the World  |  Sat, Dec 12, 2026, 8:00 pm | Azrieli Studio"
      }
    ],
    "http://ogp.me/ns#image": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "https://naccnaca-eventimages.s3.amazonaws.com/41637/rounded_corner_design_(1)__large.png"
      }
    ],
    "http://ogp.me/ns#description": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "Our three guitar virtuosos revisit holiday classics with boundless creativity, bold arrangements and a style all their own. On the program: Tchaikovsky’s spellbinding Nutcracker, the timeless warmth of Vince Guaraldi’s A Charlie Brown Christmas, and even more festive surprises! \n\nThe Montréal Guitare Trio (MG3) electrifies, moves and captivates audiences, lighting up the stage. For over 25 years, this charismatic trio has shared their contagious energy with passion and intensity. But they’re more than just guitar players. These multi-instrumentalists let the violin,..."
      }
    ],
