    "http://ogp.me/ns#title": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "Maritza | ¿Quién eres? |  Fri, Nov 20, 2026, 8:00 pm | Fourth Stage"
      }
    ],
    "http://ogp.me/ns#image": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "https://naccnaca-eventimages.s3.amazonaws.com/41618/rounded_corner_design__large.png"
      }
    ],
    "http://ogp.me/ns#description": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "El español sigue al texto en inglés\n\n¿Quién eres? (Who are you?), singer–songwriter Maritza’s show proposes a musical journey about resilience. Known for the depth of her songs and her ability to touch people’s hearts, Maritza released ¿Quién eres?, her first album in Spanish, in 2022. It’s an artistic project inspired by a process of self-empowerment. \n\nBorn in the Dominican Republic, Maritza reconnects in this show with her mother tongue, which she quickly forgot after being adopted very young by a Francophone couple from..."
      }
    ],
    "http://ogp.me/ns/fb#admins": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "728780803"
      }
