    ],
    "http://ogp.me/ns#description": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "“Time passes, and it takes its time,” as the song goes. And time has passed… More than 30 years of happily mining, here and elsewhere, the glowing embers of Quebec’s traditional repertoire; 30 years of getting together and sharing; 30 years of singing to the beat of their feet without ever losing heart; 30 years of camaraderie in unison and in harmony; 30 years of getting along and sometimes moving along. \n\nAfter all these years of joy, punctuated by the great..."
      }
    ],
